➜吃屎和洁癖并存，餐前饭后要搓手，苍蝇是怎么做到的？
http://www.sohu.com/a/415723516_624188	14456
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200831/80169ea8c66548d2bf0eae3cc9ce73eb.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在日常生活中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有这样一种生物</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它的每次出现</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都带着关乎<strong>人类尊严</strong>的巨大挑战</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200831/f4c3216bc40f4049a323685e1c470082.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它自带的<strong>嗡嗡铃声</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">总是能让人类回想起</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>没背课文却不得不面对老师抽查的恐惧</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们祈祷着盼望着</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>自己永远不会被它选中……</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟一旦被选中</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
