<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">等待你的可能是——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200831/98d81c485b144d2899f929034cc3e826.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>苍</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>蝇</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一种<strong>完全变态形态</strong>的<strong>超级变态昆虫</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最爱在你等菜齐来张全家福前</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从容落入盘中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">开始自己经典而优雅的<strong>餐前仪式</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200831/e75cc69148e440e58c68c599ba6e43b6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而这套动作</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也成了无数人人生一大疑惑——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200831/8dee9b19a7a54f9b9a3785cb728dbc03.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">带着你们的疑惑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一起走进<strong>蝇蝇怪的世界</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一探究竟</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200831/f6f40a3f1f544fa9a8c533a398b0d71c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>吃屎和洁癖，从来不违和</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">苍蝇这套餐前仪式</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其实和大部分人想的一样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就是为了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">双手对搓十几秒产生鸡屎味</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>洗 手</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200831/c996419498234aa388858236540a9817.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">至于为什么明明屎都吃了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还会在意手脏这个问题</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其实主要还是因为——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">苍蝇眼睛太大了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200831/6a9be1130df7477d90b4a5b87336eea1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟两只眼睛</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就占了差不多整张脸</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没地儿搁鼻子了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是<strong>苍蝇只好把自己的味觉感受器</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>挪到了脚上去</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200831/12e761ec56dc4fbb902e351a14592b83.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">身为最不挑食的美食家</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不管是<strong>巧克力味的屎</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还是<strong>屎味的巧克力</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">苍蝇都会亲自去品品</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">脚上难免沾上<strong>污渍</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这极大地影响了它对美味的判断</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200831/ca5e5eb13dc84b01a7dfc3ed5d3ac08d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不仅如此苍蝇的手还会分泌</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>辅助行动与降落的黏液</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要是沾的东西多了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就是<strong>变相的负重飞行</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那对于靠<strong>快</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来躲避致命攻击的苍蝇来说</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就是个死亡危机</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200831/881ef73bc0664d07a311b7284e6f99fb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为了吃得更香、活得更久</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">苍蝇养成了<strong>餐前饭后洗手</strong>的好习惯</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200831/b5f2743e5fbc4a76b370aa87b0806bf3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而如果遇上和大家一块吃饭的情况</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">苍蝇会更卖力的清洁自己</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以这样的洁癖姿态</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来<strong>吸引异性的关注</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200831/8cc84cba7d5b46b1ac2fac07a0afab66.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在餐前仪式结束后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">苍蝇就可以正式开吃了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>吸管吃固体，我只服苍蝇</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也不知道是不是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">苍蝇90%的精力</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都拿去发展自身视力了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">搞到自个儿牙齿都<strong>没长齐</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就留了个<strong>吸管</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">咬、嚼这类动作自然是做不到了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">进食就只能靠<strong>吸</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200831/a6dc3d80b4c041a6a5d2108044d530cd.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">问题来了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">固体得怎么吸——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200831/d86ae8d6c77d4f7083055c68ce354945.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">能活这么久</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人家自然有自己的办法</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那就是——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200831/f1448883fffd47428dc884dbfeb9e4f2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没错</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它吐出自己的<strong>唾液</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>和消化液的混合物</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">帮助把固态的食物变成<strong>液态</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200831/b09890474e2e42e6b92e575c95f04474.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不过食物在眼前</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">谁能不猴急?</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">况且可能有人在后面</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">伺机发动攻击</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以苍蝇不会等到食物完全液化后再吃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当差不多融成<strong>小碎块</strong>的时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它们就已经开吸了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这点嘴巴太细的蚊子就做不到了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200831/4591f09f4c444e1784a8d8caedf9568f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">吸饱后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">苍蝇搓了搓手</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">抹了一把自己的油头</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">然后开始</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>拉屎</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200831/1dadac9af3e24edc9ef1d690aa009d7c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>想要吃得更多</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>就得拉得更快</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而且平时也不是顿顿都能吃好的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有时候屎啊、腐肉啊也得吃吃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">很有可能会残留细菌</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这样边吃边拉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就能帮助苍蝇到更快的<strong>排出细菌</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">维持自身的健康</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200831/3d85643fc0b44b13b417510919c8547d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">苍蝇的一整个消化过程就结束了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽然看起来好像挺复杂</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但其实一整套下来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>7-11秒</strong>就搞定了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200831/b98f900bef06468eb1708ef6772dfec2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">至于那些</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">口水、消化液以及屎……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">苍蝇一个都没带走</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">全留在了你的食物上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200831/a74404942045448c9de51549a5dbb068.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>苍蝇的爱意，不只给了屎</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人生一大疑惑苍蝇搓腿是解决了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那么苍蝇<strong>选择谁降落</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>围绕谁飞</strong>又是怎么回事</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200831/6bea4d4acde747b99573f1b879ba7c9d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽说都被人叫做苍蝇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但人家还是有很多种类的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">和人类日常息息相关的大致有三类</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">啥都想要来一口的<strong>家中常客</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200831/0031d7d7165b409b8c6ce74c30fcbfe4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">被人类研究得最彻底的<strong>科学献身者</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200831/c0a62bc50eb849808da3b01b58e26047.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以及</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">自带流行金属光泽的<strong>粪坑爱好者</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200831/6033331659944508a2e6d438639cdc31.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它们的喜好各不相同</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200831/ad305c0c80d244b9840271901960bf99.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">除了各自喜好外</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">对汗这种<strong>咸口</strong>的东西</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大家都很爱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟<strong>平常盐分摄入不足</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">能吸点儿咸味的是一点</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以<strong>新陈代谢</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>出汗多</strong>的人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">更容易被苍蝇们盯上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200831/159fb7a88e4d4000892e0ee4937ce6b2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再配合上喜好表</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我们可以推测一下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">围绕你身边的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">——如果是家蝇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那它更可能是被<strong>汗</strong>吸引的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">——如果是黑腹果蝇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那可能是因为你<strong>甜甜的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">——如果是丽蝇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200831/5db510b3dfe94c03bb0ea8872d699abf.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>打还是不打，这是个问题</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其实</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大家也不用那么嫌弃苍蝇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一见就想给人家来套<strong>屠蝇十八掌</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">首先</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人家那对<strong>36D</strong>的眼睛不是白长的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">接近<strong>360°的视野范围</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你想打？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200831/e1aa4e56812a4923b23af366bc8a18a7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其次</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">苍蝇和蚊子比起来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">肉感多了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有的<strong>虱子</strong>甚至会把苍蝇当做工具人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">附在上面感受<strong>坐飞机的快乐</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你要是一巴掌下去</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一尸两命<strong>双倍爆浆</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">摊开手那场面</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200831/6c40a46c14d040c2890dbbe2988b3b16.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">像家蝇这种长期出入垃圾场</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">身上附着一堆<strong>病菌微生物</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在你的饭上呕吐又拉屎</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让你在人群中丢脸</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200831/12654fee1dbc4b179108813396041b88.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">——它们不吸血啊</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而你也不太可能吃了它们</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这样你们之间就缺乏了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>负距离的接触机会</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">靠停在身上和食物上搓腿的方式</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">传播病毒效率和<strong>蚊子</strong>比起来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">真是<strong>低太多了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200831/bb2a7d587389441fa9ba30770d5f4e60.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而苍蝇的孩子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>蛆</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽说长得恶心</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但比蚊子的孩子用处大多了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可以说是<strong>大自然最良心的清洁工</strong>了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">勤勤恳恳分解垃圾把自己养<strong>月半</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">然后用胖胖的自己<strong>喂饱了一堆动物</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而它们爱吃腐食这个点</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还被充分利用来<strong>处理伤口</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无菌的蛆虫可以帮忙快速清创</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200831/55b8fa06cac84890a8169954e657a055.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">除此之外</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">蛆还能<strong>帮助法医推断死亡时间</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">做成<strong>高营养饲料</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为牲畜们补充蛋白质变得更好吃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>——真是燃烧自己照亮他人</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200831/75df1d3e30394dc890fec324aa8f63d1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">然而</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>说了这么多你们这些人类会关心吗？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不，你不会</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你只关心</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>如何打提高打蝇成功率</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">朕都懂</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">拿走不谢</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200831/cd2a7a83fb6343048b0a54d899dc8773.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200831/4d2a976b32db4d249861b3a01a651308.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200831/3cd82e17843c4895be2183d13ef9aa54.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>